Author: yubrew
Title: Online communities, who's got it right?
Content:
Everyone knows about the rise and fall of Slashdot, Digg, reddit. There are so many ways that _might_ work...

Are there any examples of lasting communities that still produce high quality posts? SomethingAwful comes to mind.
